{"tid":1613192,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"摺紙=和理非活動=Be humble好嘛？","createTime":"2019-10-02T13:04:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-02T15:24:20.000Z","uid":229880,"like":100,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"4930fc51a748d2ff6112cff5149e72312ba6dc54","tid":1613192,"uid":229880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T13:04:34.000Z","msg":"唔係想分化，亦好理解大家好憤怒、好有壓力，<br />\n<br />\n但摺紙係和平活動，點解會變左狂屌人影相<br />\n<br />\n好多阿叔阿嬸特登走過黎想支持下<br />\n<br />\n佢地離遠影完一張相，share俾佢地同溫層<br />\n<br />\n效果點都比我地文宣效果大<br />\n<br />\n同時，畫面人多、和平摺紙，就正正顯示我地能收能放。<br />\n<br />\n點解都可以變左狂屌人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XCJ2wWk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXCJ2wWk.jpg&h=64de3fe9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家可以be humble嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n記得大家係點樣多元抗爭走到依家嘛<br />\n<br />\n諒解手足壓力，但唔係個個人明的<br />\n<br />\n如果好怕可以包住摺，更加顯示白色恐佈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n願榮光歸香港<br />\n<br />\n大家加油"},{"pid":"744a1f847fe0f8f14d8c28ae585544f45606d975","tid":1613192,"uid":229880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T13:04:47.000Z","msg":"自推1/5"},{"pid":"1d74330ab6d274a4af675f7a117915185a07c088","tid":1613192,"uid":229880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T13:05:07.000Z","msg":"自推2/5"},{"pid":"d2f7bdc9c29a2ce5e69235c21b711dd7d8b4577e","tid":1613192,"uid":192824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T13:05:37.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"5791c1dc239ade570a20e011d3f1d9ab53eeac04","tid":1613192,"uid":229880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T13:05:49.000Z","msg":"自推3/5"},{"pid":"e3bdeaebf13dfbfa2219eeb30e32aeb37d6daa41","tid":1613192,"uid":229880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"r