\n==========<br />\n今次我地好彩有美國幫手<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">咁下次呢?</span><br />\n確保槍權先算係香港人嘅最終勝利<br />\n嫌太長直接睇#3<br />\n<br />\n[長文]香港警察的清算及其暴動的可能性，真普選是否足夠，防止暴政再現及港人槍權<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1612769\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1612769</a>"},{"pid":"f337cebaa648a95e4096bcf4728c09235399fbbb","tid":1613192,"uid":291065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T13:21:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"079572ec0f6b79fe02160e65340969d0d51248d7","tid":1613192,"uid":216603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T13:21:20.000Z","msg":"幫樓主補番句<br />\n不完美, 可接受, 有改善空間<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"421d021688510e72992d83958f85279279b98b54","tid":1613192,"uid":126626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T13:21:30.000Z","msg":"其實大家好嬲好正常，但難得吸引人過嚟做到效果，就無謂屌走人啦"},{"pid":"831e0865ab7fed1dbe964074459e04d864017f49","tid":1613192,"uid":199712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T13:21:36.000Z","msg":"tui"},{"pid":"bb86f3c39e6e49c610fb5a5384d56d0ff2ab15e7","tid":1613192,"uid":303648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T13:21:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2924c2f3586191c8d8dd99f96d9cd04852eeec77","tid":1613192,"uid":82536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T13:22:06.000Z","msg":"tui"},{"pid":"5d953e9ce55e0ae329d86ded91e6e69c37b8bca7","tid":1613192,"uid":38548,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"079572ec0f6b79fe02160e65340969d0d51248d7","tid":1613192,"uid":216603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T13:21:20.000Z","msg":"幫樓主補番句<br />\n不完美, 可接受, 有改善空間<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T13:22:17.000Z","msg":"今次真係不能接受<br />\n<br />\n講左三個月都唔肯改<br />\n<br />\n政治要爭取他人認同<br />\n<br />\n冇公關他人點認同你？"},{"pid":"690bb0336db4c74dd99e1de3fb827a08d